caption: Tribute to this great man. Garden surrounded by a gate with a simple plaque, without a cross or slab, according to his wishes: where his ashes were mixed with the earth (with exemption from the City of Paris).
Respect to Mr. Cyclopède and to the prosecutor of the Tribunal des Flangrants Délires. Pierre and his wife rest in this simple and moving tomb. Located very close to the tomb of Frédéric Chopin
